Ignore all history files (anything under `Only for History Use/` is not authoritative for builds or copy).

**Repository index:** Root **[`AGENTS.md`](../../AGENTS.md)** maps rule categories, key directories, hooks, workspace settings, **Cursor rule precedence**, global Rules-for-AI snippet, and **index resync** after refactors.

The active rules are divided into **`design-system.mdc`** (full **V7** layout, Z-order, tonal rhythm, mandatory assets, spacing tokens, typography, motion, palette, §8 composition, accessibility, hero-metrics pattern), **`copy-writing.mdc`** (volume pivots, content mapping, copy-facing audit), and **`seo-strategy.mdc`** (metadata, technical SEO, DOM/heading integrity). **Globs** attach these modules across **`app/`**, **`components/`**, **`lib/`**, **`public/`**, and matching extensions — see each file’s YAML frontmatter.

Mandatory enforcement (self-audit, Git sync on `main`): see **`glc-modular-enforcement-cloud-safety.mdc`**.

**Project hooks:** **[`.cursor/hooks.json`](../../.cursor/hooks.json)** and **[`.cursor/hooks/`](../../.cursor/hooks/)** (optional `sessionStart` drain script).

**Service images:** All service photography lives under **`public/images/services/`** in subfolders that match each service line (`Drainage-and-Hardscaping`, `Excavation`, `Foundations`, `Grading`, `Hauling`, `Snow Removal`). Full conventions and URL encoding: **`design-system.mdc`** (Service photography).

**Section depth, palette, and assets:** **≥3 contrasting layers**, **tri-tonal type**, **≥3 GLC palette roles**, **mandatory visuals per section** unless `disableAssets`, tonal alternation — **`design-system.mdc` §1–2, §4, §8**.

**Rule files in this folder:** `index.mdc`, `glc-modular-enforcement-cloud-safety.mdc`, `design-system.mdc`, `copy-writing.mdc`, `seo-strategy.mdc`.
